function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idDawoodFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_NPC_Kehj_KIA_IronWolf_Follower")
	idAsaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AsaFollower")

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaFollower) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idDawoodFollower) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_LonelyWolf_03a, idActor, idAsaFollower, idDawoodFollower)
	end


	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idDawoodFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idDawoodFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idDawoodFollower, actor_DawoodNearEntrance, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idDawoodFollower, actor_DawoodNearEntrance)
		Hydra.QActorDelete(idDawoodFollower)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idAsaFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAsaFollower, actor_AsaNearEntrance, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idAsaFollower, actor_AsaNearEntrance)
		Hydra.QActorDelete(idAsaFollower)
	end

end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(fx_CameraShake, "Shake_Sml", idActorPlayer)
	
	idAsaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_AsaNearEntrance)
	idDawoodClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_DawoodNearEntrance)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaClone) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_LonelyWolf_03b, idActorPlayer, idAsaClone)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idAsaClone, conv_LonelyWolf_03b)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAsaClone, loc_Dungeon, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idAsaClone, 1.5)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idDawoodClone) then
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idDawoodClone, conv_LonelyWolf_03b)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idDawoodClone, loc_Dungeon, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idDawoodClone, 1.5)
	end

end

function Start()
	idAsaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_AsaInterrogation)
	idDawoodClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_DawoodInterrogation)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAsaClone, loc_AsaInterrogationWalkTo, "NPC_Walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idAsaClone, 1.5)
	end

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idDawoodClone) then
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idDawoodClone)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idDawoodClone, loc_AsaInterrogationWalkTo, "NPC_Walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idDawoodClone, 1.5)
	end
end
